Package cern.accsoft.steering.jmad.domain.result.tfs

Interface TfsSummary

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TfsSummaryImpl
    public interface TfsSummary
    An implementation of this interface shall contain all the information which is available in the Twiss-summary of madx. i.e. in the header of a tfs-file.

    In general the values in here are a representation of the values of the summary table of MadX.
